# Knowledge Index Maintenance Skill Equivalent

- Treat `ai-rule-learner` as the primary owner of the global knowledge index.
- Keep `.ai/personalities/README.md` explicit about the structural system personas.
- Keep `.ai/knowledge-index/README.md` as the human-readable entrypoint.
- Rebuild `.ai/knowledge-index/INDEX.md` with `./scripts/rebuild-knowledge-index.ps1` after structural changes.
- Use `./scripts/catalog-agent-asset.ps1` to append new archive records for index-facing assets.
- Keep Copilot, Claude Code, and Cursor behavior aligned and record support in `SUPPORTED.md`.